ActFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
SubjectLands in part of the Military Reserve within Tecumseh Park, in Chatham-Kent, Ontario. ** Declassification **
PrecisOrder declaring that certain LANDS forming part of the military reserve now known as TECUMSEH PARK, located in the Municipality of CHATHAM-KENT, Ontario, are no longer necessary for the defence of Canada.
